        GREETINGS_ADVENTURER_I_M_SO_GLAD_YOU_VE                              = 6842,  -- Greetings adventurer! I'm so glad you've come, kupo! To celebrate the safe recovery of all eleven of King Kupofried's mog tablets, we're offering a limited-time teleportation service for the low, low price of # gil! What do you say?
