        AH_ARE_YOU_FROM_THE_RHINOSTERY                                       = 7099,  -- Ah! Are you from the Rhinostery?
        YOU_RE_NOT_SPITTING_DHALMELS_I_WISH_THEY                             = 7100,  -- You're not? Spitting dhalmels! I wish they would hurry-wurry!
        COULD_YOU_COME_BACK_WHEN_IT_S_DARK                                   = 7101,  -- Could you come back when it's dark? I know it's a bother-wother, but I was specifically instructed not to take it out during the day.
        OH_YOU_RE_THE_PERSON_FROM_THE_RHINOSTERY                             = 7102,  -- Oh, you're the person from the Rhinostery? I've been waiting for you!
        I_GUESS_IT_S_A_REALLY_IMPORTANT_PARCEL                               = 7103,  -- I guess it's a really important parcel-morsel. I had to follow all these rules when I was handling it! Thankfully, it's really small, so it was easy to carry.
        I_HEAR_YOU_HAVE_SOME_PRETTY_STRICT_RESTRICTIONS                      = 7104,  -- I hear you have some pretty strict restrictions you have to follow, too. You should leave immediately, and don't get distracted on the way to the Rhinostery!
        AH_NICE_TO_SEE_YOU_AGAIN_DID_YOU                                     = 7105,  -- Ah! Nice to see you again! Did you manage to deliver that parcel-morsel on time?
        I_M_EKOKOKO_THE_GOVERNOR_OF_THIS_LITTLE                              = 7106,  -- I'm Ekokoko, the governor of this little town. There isn't much to see, but you're welcome to stay as long as you want.
        IF_THERE_IS_ANYTHING_YOU_WISH_TO_KNOW                                = 7107,  -- If there is anything you wish to know about Mhaura, ask my aide, Numi Adaligo. She's right over there.
        IT_S_TOUGH_GETTING_ENOUGH_FOOD_TO_FEED                               = 7108,  -- It's tough getting enough food to feed everyone these days, with all those monsters prowling the areas near the town.
        REALLY_WE_RE_NOT_SLACKIN_OFF_EVER_SINCE                              = 7109,  -- Really, we're not slackin' off. Ever since th' airship shippin' routes opened, hasn't been much fer guys like us to do, ya know?
        I_M_BORED_MAYBE_I_SHOULD_MOVE_TO                                     = 7110,  -- I'm bored... Maybe I should move to a city in a country with a little more life. Say, how're things where you come from?
        WELCOME                                                              = 7111,  -- Welcome!
        I750T_J                                                              = 7112,  -- |`i750t[j
        ACCEPT_THIS_REQUEST_YES_NO                                           = 7113,  -- Accept this request? Yes. No.
        THIS_IS_A_SMALL_TOWN_BUT_WE_GET                                      = 7114,  -- This is a small town, but we get a lot of traffic because of the port. We have to stay alert and try to stop trrrouble before it starts.
