        I_CAN_T_LET_YOU_THROUGH_THIS_DOOR                                    = 7116,  -- I can't let you through this door. This is the guards' barrrracks. No unauthorized people allowed.
        YOU_CAN_T_TELL_IF_YOU_RE_IN                                          = 7117,  -- You can't tell if you're in the town, but I hearrr the beastmen are up to something out there. How are things where you come from?
        I_AM_HYRIA_THE_CAPTAIN_OF_THE_GUARD                                  = 7118,  -- I am Hyria, the captain of the guard here in Mhaura. My duty is to protect the governor from harm.
        YOU_CAN_SEE_THE_WHOLE_OF_THE_HARBOR                                  = 7119,  -- You can see the whole of the harbor and town from here. I like watching the port especially. There are so many different kinds of people getting on and off the ships there.
        YOU_MAY_NOT_BELIEVE_ME_BUT_BEFORE_AIRSHIPS                           = 7120,  -- You may not believe me, but before airships started to fly, this inn was packed all year round.
        THOSE_DAYS_ARE_LONG_PAST_AND_THIS_TOWN                               = 7121,  -- Those days are long past, and this town is a little on the dingy side now, but we Mhaurans haven't changed. Some of us have our quirks, but we all still welcome travelers with open arms.
        WELCOME_TO_THE_SAILORRR_S_STAY_IF_YOU                                = 7122,  -- Welcome to the Sailorrr's Stay! If you need armor or shields, we got those, too! Just talk to Graine here, and she'll show you our wares!
        AND_IF_YOU_NEED_WEAPONS_GO_SEE_RUNITO                                = 7123,  -- And if you need weapons, go see Runito-Monito upstairrrs! He's got the meanest weapons this side of the Bastore Sea!
        ANYTHING_TO_DECLARE_NO_GOOD_YOU_MAY_PASS                             = 7124,  -- Anything to declare? No? Good. you may pass.
