        SIR_NEREUS_HERE_IS_THE_FOREMOST_AUTHORITY_ON                         = 7170,  -- Sir Nereus here is the foremost authority on ceramics, and I came all the way from San d'Oria to become his student, but...Sir Nereus is a hard man to please.
        AS_YOU_CAN_SEE_CERAMICS_IS_ONE_OF                                    = 7171,  -- As you can see, ceramics is one of Mhaura's main exports. I'm glad I always have work as a longshoreman, but I wish they'd stop making me carry all the heavy ones...
