        I_M_TIRED_OF_ALWAYS_BEING_ON_THE                                     = 7248,  -- I'm tired of always being on the move. I just want to settle down somewhere and take it easy in my twilight years.
        AH_YES_I_REMEMBER_YOU_YOU_WERE_ONE                                   = 7249,  -- Ah yes, I remember you. You were one of the thieves from the Tenshodo gathering. Isn't this a coincidence? What business have you in Mhaura?
        HMM_YOU_SAY_YOU_HAVE_SOMETHING_TO_ASK                                = 7250,  -- Hmm? You say you have something to ask me?
        I_LL_TELL_YOU_RIGHT_UP_FRONT_IF                                      = 7251,  -- I'll tell you right up front. If you want me to help you in the Atarefaunet treasure hunt, I'll need to know the names of the people working with you.
        I_SEEM_TO_HAVE_BEEN_A_LITTLE_HASTY                                   = 7252,  -- I seem to have been a little hasty in my judgment. So many of our fellow thieves are falling over each other out there trying to find that treasure.
        WELL_THIS_IS_UNEXPECTED_YOU_WANT_ME_TO                               = 7253,  -- Well, this is unexpected. You want me to tell you the name signed on the papers I handed in for that last job?
        I_MUST_APOLOGIZE_BUT_I_CAN_T_SEEM                                    = 7254,  -- ...I must apologize, but I can't seem to remember it too clearly. I wonder why that is?
        I_MAY_BE_ABLE_TO_JOG_MY_MEMORY                                       = 7255,  -- I may be able to jog my memory if you do me a favor. Go to Garlaige Citadel and defeat a particularly nasty bomb that is hiding up in the ceiling.
        FIND_THE_HOLES_IN_THE_CEILING_AND_TRY                                = 7256,  -- Find the holes in the ceiling and try burning this % underneath them. The bomb should be smoked out of its hiding place. Defeating it should be a walk in the park for an adventurer like you.
        ONE_MORE_THING_I_M_GOING_TO_NEED                                     = 7257,  -- ...One more thing. I'm going to need some evidence that you've really defeated the bomb. According to rumor, that particular bomb should drop %.
        IF_YOU_BRING_THAT_BACK_TO_ME_I                                       = 7258,  -- If you bring that back to me, I'll make more of an effort to recall what you want to know. Good luck.
        DEFEAT_THE_BOISTEROUS_BOMB_LURKING_IN_THE_CEILING                    = 7259,  -- Defeat the boisterous bomb lurking in the ceiling of Garlaige Citadel and bring me % as evidence that the task is done.
        FIND_THE_HOLES_IN_THE_CEILING_AND_TRY_2                              = 7260,  -- Find the holes in the ceiling and try burning this % underneath them. The bomb should be smoked out of its hiding place.
        BE_CAREFUL_ADVENTURER                                                = 7261,  -- Be careful, adventurer.
        WELL_DONE_ADVENTURER_YOU_COULD_MAKE_MONSTER_EXTERMINATION            = 7262,  -- Well done, adventurer. You could make monster extermination a new career.
        NOW_THAT_YOU_VE_COMPLETED_YOUR_TASK_I                                = 7263,  -- Now that you've completed your task, I seem to have remembered something. The signature on my papers was the letter D.
        YOU_KNOW_MOST_THIEVES_ARE_A_GREEDY_BUNCH                             = 7264,  -- You know, most thieves are a greedy bunch...your kind is rare. Aren't you salivating over this Atarefaunet treasure like everybody else?
        NO_YOUR_KIND_IS_THE_MOST_DANGEROUS_HAVE                              = 7265,  -- No...Your kind is the most dangerous... Have to be careful around you... You pretend not to have the slightest interest and then snatch up the prize while everyone's backs are turned...
        WELL_YOU_RE_NOT_GOING_TO_FOOL_ME                                     = 7266,  -- Well, you're not going to fool me. I'm done talking with you, so be on your way.
        THE_TENSHODO_IS_TREATING_THIS_TALK_OF_THE                            = 7267,  -- The Tenshodo is treating this talk of the Atarefaunet treasure as just another rumor. To spread this far, though, there must be a kernel of truth to it.
        IF_YOU_RE_GOING_TO_JOIN_THE_RACE                                     = 7268,  -- If you're going to join the race for the treasure, you might want to hire yourself a bodyguard. Sometimes these things can turn into a bloody free-for-all.
        THE_SHIP_BOUND_FOR_SELBINA_WILL_IN_IN                                = 7269,  -- The ship bound for Selbina will [arrive/depart] in [less than an hour/about 1 hour/about 2 hours/about 3 hours/about 4 hours/about 5 hours/about 6 hours/about 7 hours] (# [minute/minutes] in Earth time).
        THE_SHIP_BOUND_FOR_SELBINA_IS_NOW                                    = 7270,  -- The ship bound for Selbina is now [arriving/departing].
        THE_SHIP_BOUND_FOR_AL_ZAHBI_WILL_IN                                  = 7271,  -- The ship bound for Al Zahbi will [arrive/depart] in [less than an hour/about 1 hour/about 2 hours/about 3 hours/about 4 hours/about 5 hours/about 6 hours/about 7 hours] (# [minute/minutes] in Earth time).
        THE_SHIP_BOUND_FOR_AL_ZAHBI_IS_NOW                                   = 7272,  -- The ship bound for Al Zahbi is now [arriving/departing].
        OLD_WOUNDS_ACHE_ON_DAYS_LIKE_THESE_NOBODY                            = 7273,  -- Old wounds ache on days like these. Nobody wants to give in to the march of years, I guess...
        AND_YOU_ARRRE                                                        = 7274,  -- And you arrre?
        WEREN_T_YOU_THE_ONE_UNDER_ORDERRRS_FROM                              = 7275,  -- Weren't you the one under orderrrs from Chieftainness Perih Vashai?
        THE_MITHRAN_TRACKER_FROM_THE_HOMELAND_WAS_HERE                       = 7276,  -- The Mithran Tracker from the homeland was here a moment ago. She was asking about the incident that occurred twenty years ago concerning the Chieftainness of the Fire Tribe and her daughter...
        DO_YOU_KNOW_OF_THE_FIRE_TRIBE_THEY                                   = 7277,  -- Do you know of the Fire Tribe? They are a Mithran tribe that lives on the southern continent.
        IT_WAS_SOME_THIRTY_YEARS_AGO_NOW_THE                                 = 7278,  -- It was some thirty years ago now. The chieftainness of that tribe committed the sin of slaying a fellow tribal member.
        SHE_SPENT_TEN_YEARS_ATONING_FOR_THAT_SIN                             = 7279,  -- She spent ten years atoning for that sin in the homeland... When war broke out here, she escaped from prison, crossing over to this continent with her daughter in tow.
        AT_THE_TIME_I_WAS_PERFORMING_THE_DANGEROUS                           = 7280,  -- At the time, I was performing the dangerous duty of escorting people and supplies between Jeuno and Windurst.
        ONE_DAY_A_MITHRAN_WOMAN_AND_HER_CHILD                                = 7281,  -- One day, a Mithran woman and her child slipped into our company.
        WE_SET_OUT_FOR_JEUNO_NOT_REALIZING_IT                                = 7282,  -- We set out for Jeuno, not realizing it was the chieftainness and her daughter who had joined us.
        HOWEVER_THINGS_DIDN_T_GO_AS_PLANNED_WE                               = 7283,  -- However, things didn't go as planned. We were discovered by a party of Yagudo in the Meriphataud Mountains.
        THE_YAGUDO_QUICKLY_OVERWHELMED_US_AND_WE_WERE                        = 7284,  -- The Yagudo quickly overwhelmed us, and we were taken to Castle Oztroja and held as prisoners.
        THE_PRISON_OF_OZTROJA_WAS_A_TERRIBLE_PLACE                           = 7285,  -- The prison of Oztroja was a terrible place. All we could do was shiver in the biting cold.
        AT_REGULAR_INTERVALS_THE_YAGUDO_WOULD_COME_TO                        = 7286,  -- At regular intervals, the Yagudo would come to drag one of us from the prison.
        FINALLY_THE_CHIEFTAINNESS_OF_THE_FIRE_TRIBE_WAS                      = 7287,  -- Finally, the Chieftainness of the Fire Tribe was taken away, leaving her daughter behind. Only the two of us were left...
        ID_7288                                                              = 7288,  -- ......
        NOT_LONG_AFTER_THAT_WE_WERE_SAVED_BY                                 = 7289,  -- Not long after that, we were saved by the elite warriors stationed in the Meriphataud Mountains, led by Perih Vashai herself.
        I_TOOK_THE_CHILD_BACK_TO_JEUNO_BUT                                   = 7290,  -- I took the child back to Jeuno, but she grew thinner by the day from misery and exhaustion.
        HER_BODY_WAS_INTERRED_IN_THE_ELDIEME_NECROPOLIS                      = 7291,  -- ...Her body was interred in the Eldieme Necropolis, along with the remains of the other races who had died in the war.
