        YOU_ARE_AN_ADVENTURER_ARE_YOU_NOT_MY                                 = 7739,  -- You are an adventurer, are you not? My name is Wilhelm. I am a purchasing agent for the Brugaire Consortium.
        I_HAVE_QUITE_A_BIT_OF_RESPECT_FOR                                    = 7740,  -- I have quite a bit of respect for you adventurers. I think it is marvelous that there are people in this world who are doing their best to help others.
        THIS_IS_JUST_A_PASSING_RUMOR_BUT_I                                   = 7741,  -- This is just a passing rumor, but I heard that several people have ventured to another world and encountered extraordinary beings...in a mysterious place, enveloped in light!
        IT_IS_QUITE_A_FAR_FETCHED_TALE_IF                                    = 7742,  -- It is quite a far-fetched tale, if I say so myself! It would seem that such an absurd story cannot be true, and asking if you have been to such a land would be utterly ludicrous...but still, I cannot hold back my curiosity, if indeed you have seen this ethereal land.
