        BY_ALTANA_YOU_ARE_FAR_MORE_COURAGEOUS_THAN                           = 7745,  -- By Altana! You are far more courageous than the average adventurer! Then tell me, have you seen the giant black beasts which do not seem to be living creatures, but machines with flesh and blood?
