        FEAST_YOUR_EYES_UPON_ME_THE_MASTER_WASTER                            = 7839,  -- Feast your eyes upon me, the master-waster of a thousand runes, straightaru from the alleys of Adoulin! The one, the only, Zurko-Bazurko!
        HUHN_HUHHHN_OF_COURSE_A_WIMP_LIKE_YOU                                = 7840,  -- Huhn huhhhn. Of course a wimp like you would want to come bask in the radiance of a living-wiving legend like the Zurk. Do you want his autograph as--whoa-ho, is that %?
        AH_SO_YOU_RE_THE_GREENHORN_ANASTASE_WAS                              = 7841,  -- Ah, so you're the greenhorn Anastase was flip-flapping about.
        DON_T_GET_YOUR_PANTALOONS_IN_A_BUNCHY                                = 7842,  -- Don't get your pantaloons in a bunchy-wunch. The Zurk's already found the geomagnetic field you're looking for. How? Because he's perfection incarnate.
        SO_YOU_GONNA_ATTUNE_THAT_THING_TO_THIS                               = 7843,  -- So, you gonna attune that thing to this spotaru or what?
        OHOHO_THE_ZURK_LIKES_YOUR_STYLE_ADVENTURER_HE                        = 7844,  -- Ohoho, the Zurk likes your style, adventurer. He can always sympathize with those who like to defy fate. The Zurk himself doesn't play by anyone's rulesy-wules...not even his own.
        THE_OBVIOUS_CHOICE_BUT_THE_ZURK_ABIDES_NOW                           = 7845,  -- The obvious choice, but the Zurk abides. Now put your % on the ground here and wait for the action-waction to unfold.
