        OF_COURSE_NO_MERE_MORTAL_COULD_UNDERSTAND_THE                        = 7849,  -- Of course, no mere mortal could understand the complex configurations of this waypointaru. That's why the Zurk, also known throughout Adoulin as the Second Coming of the Occult, will condescend to--
        WHAT_MASTER_ANASTASE_WANTS_A_REPORTARU_FROM_THE                      = 7850,  -- What!? Master Anastase wants a reportaru from the Zurk!?
        EVERYONE_KNOWS_YOU_RE_NOT_SUPPOSED_TO_INTERRUPTARU                   = 7851,  -- Everyone knows you're not supposed to interruptaru the hero during his speech! What a terrible sense of timing you have.
        NOW_THAT_YOU_VE_KILLED_THE_MOMENT_UM                                 = 7852,  -- Now that you've killed the moment...um...this waypoint isn't up to snuffy-wuff yet, so...
        JUST_TELL_HIM_THAT_THE_ZURK_S_EMPLOYING                              = 7853,  -- Just tell him that the Zurk's employing every onz of his decisiveness, determination, and most importantly, his daring-waring to save the day!
        ALSO_BE_SURE_TO_MENTION_THAT_THE_SLIGHTEST                           = 7854,  -- Also be sure to mention that the slightest-wightest disruption in the Zurk's concentration can resultaru in Vana'diel's complete decimation...so he won't be making any reports for a while.
        THE_FATE_OF_THE_WORLD_HANGS_IN_THE                                   = 7855,  -- The fate of the world hangs in the balance, understand!? You're to report that the Zurk is on a mission of the most epic-wepic proportions for the good of all mankind. There is no other option.
        HNNNG_THE_ZURK_CAN_FEEL_IT_THE_RUNE                                  = 7856,  -- Hnnng! The Zurk can feel it! The rune from which his unfathomable powers derive is about to eruptaru! Must...suppress...its eldritch-weldritch energy! The prophesied time...is yet to come!
        WH_WHATEVER_CAN_THIS_BE_FROM_AN_OBSIDIAN                             = 7857,  -- Wh-whatever can this be...!? From an obsidian-widian darkness flows a malicious outpouring of flavor that assaultarus the tongue with an overpowering sweetness!
        HMPH_YOUR_NAIVETY_AMUSES_ME_NO_MATTER_HOW                            = 7858,  -- Hmph, your naivety amuses me. No matter how much you whine, the Zurk cannot return what has willingly given-wiven itself up to his soul!
        THOSE_EYES_BRIMMING_WITH_TEARS_OF_DESIRE_ONLY                        = 7859,  -- Those eyes brimming with tears of desire! Only a complete coward would actually exploit an adversary's weakness! Here, take this confection and departaru from the Zurk's presence! You disgust him!
        THESE_DAZZLING_RUNEY_WUNES_ATTRACT_SO_MANY_ADORING                   = 7860,  -- These dazzling runey-wunes attract so many adoring fans that the Zurk can barely keep count! Have you come for an autograph?
