        AN_ADVENTURER_ARE_YOU_NOT_PERHAPS_IT_WOULD                           = 8039,  -- An adventurer, are you not? Perhaps it would behoove you to speak to our esteemed governor.
        THERE_IS_DOUBTLESS_A_MOUNTAIN_OF_WORK_AROUND                         = 8040,  -- There is doubtless a mountain of work around here that needs a steady hand. Somo Aatsula can show you the way.
        AH_YOU_MUST_BE_THE_ADVENTURER_THE_GOVERNOR                           = 8041,  -- Ah, you must be the adventurer the governor was looking for!
        SHE_HAS_BEEN_PUTTING_OUT_A_CALL_FOR                                  = 8042,  -- She has been putting out a call for days now--see if you can lend her a hand.
        WHAT_DO_YOU_WISH_TO_KNOW_YOU_RE                                      = 8043,  -- What do you wish to know? You're searching for adventurers? Tell me about Mhaura. Any shops or guilds in town? Where can I find some work? Nothing for now.
        AH_I_WAS_TOLD_TO_EXPECT_SOMEONE_NAMED                                = 8044,  -- Ah, I was told to expect someone named %. Would that be you?
        FORGIVE_ME_FOR_NOT_RECOGNIZING_YOU_SOONER_I                          = 8045,  -- Forgive me for not recognizing you sooner. I had been told to be on the lookout and usher you into the governor's office without delay.
        OH_THIS_IS_WONDERFUL_INDEED_I_WAS_WORRIED                            = 8046,  -- Oh, this is wonderful, indeed! I was worried I'd have to hunt and peck for you all down the coast.
        I_EKOKOKO_SERVE_AS_THE_GOVERNOR_OF_OUR                               = 8047,  -- I, Ekokoko, serve as the governor of our bright town.
        TRUTH_BE_TOLD_I_WAS_NOT_THE_ONE                                      = 8048,  -- Truth be told, I was not the one who sought you out. No, that would be Gilgamesh, one of Vana'diel's most renowned pir--er, entrepreneurs.
        SOMETHING_ABOUT_SETTING_SAIL_AND_FINDING_SOMEONE_LOST                = 8049,  -- Something about setting sail and finding someone lost at sea? Bah, I never had much of a head for details.
        WHAT_I_DO_KNOW_IS_THAT_YOUR_NAME                                     = 8050,  -- What I do know is that your name came up on more than one occasion.
        HE_ALSO_MENTIONED_SOMETHING_ABOUT_WANTING_YOU_TO                     = 8051,  -- He also mentioned something about wanting you to procure some % from mandragoras around the Crag of Mea before you meet him.
        HE_HOPES_TO_USE_IT_TO_CREATE_A                                       = 8052,  -- He hopes to use it to create a special herbal remedy for his crew--er, associates.
        THE_WORLD_HAS_BEEN_BURSTING_AT_THE_SEAMS                             = 8053,  -- The world has been bursting at the seams with odd news these days, and frankly, none of us here can make heads or tails of it all.
        AND_MHAURA_HAS_FELT_THE_EFFECTS_PARTICULARLY_HARD                    = 8054,  -- And Mhaura has felt the effects particularly hard--our supply of % has been dwindling.
        I_LL_CALL_GILGAMESH_BACK_TO_PORT_IMMEDIATELY                         = 8055,  -- I'll call Gilgamesh back to port immediately.
        IN_THE_MEANTIME_ROUGH_UP_SOME_OF_THOSE                               = 8056,  -- In the meantime, rough up some of those mandragoras and come back with three %.
