        STEEL_YOURSELVES_FOR_OUR_LATESTARU_CREATION_AMBUSCADE                = 8166,  -- Steel yourselves for our latestaru creation--Ambuscade!
        IN_AMBUSCADE_YOU_LL_SQUARE_OFF_AGAINSTARU_A                          = 8167,  -- In Ambuscade, you'll square off againstaru a bevy of foes just chomping at the bit to see you torn into itty-bitty pieces!
        EVERY_MONTH_EARTH_TIME_NEW_CHALLENGERS_ENTER_THE                     = 8168,  -- Every month (Earth time), new challengers enter the arena, providing different challenges from the month before.
        NOW_NOW_WIPE_THAT_DRIBBLE_OFF_YOUR_CHIN                              = 8169,  -- Now, now, wipe that dribble off your chin, for there are a couple hoops-woops we're going to make you jump through before you can join.
        FIRST_YOU_MUST_BE_IN_A_PARTY_OF                                      = 8170,  -- First, you must be in a party of up to six players.
        SECOND_YOU_MUST_BE_IN_POSSESSION_OF_EITHER                           = 8171,  -- Second, you must be in possession of either % or %. Either of the two will suffice.
        THESE_TWO_GOODIES_CAN_BE_PROCURED_BY_COMPLETARUING                   = 8172,  -- These two goodies can be procured by completaruing specific Records of Eminence objectives.
        YOU_MIGHTARU_THINK_THOSE_TASKS_TO_BE_LAUGHABLY                       = 8173,  -- You mightaru think those tasks to be laughably simple, but trust me--it keeps out the riffraff. When you're prepared, examine the Ambuscade tome and be on your way.
        AND_NOW_I_WOULD_LIKE_TO_DISCUSS_THE                                  = 8174,  -- And now, I would like to discuss the rewards.
        SIMPLY_PUT_ALL_YOU_NEED_TO_KNOW_IS                                   = 8175,  -- Simply put, all you need to know is that victory in Ambuscade will reward you with a special currency known as hallmarks.
        THERE_ARE_TWO_VARIETIES_OF_REWARD_AVAILABLE_THOSE                    = 8176,  -- There are two varieties of reward available: those that are purchasable in exchange for a certain number of hallmarks, and those you receive once you have reached a particular-wicular running total of hallmarks.
        IF_YOU_RE_INCLINED_TO_JOIN_FORCES_WITH                               = 8177,  -- If you're inclined to join forces with other player-wayers, you'll receive an even more special currency known as gallantry.
        IT_GOES_WITHOUTARU_SAYING_THAT_THERE_ARE_SPECIAL                     = 8178,  -- It goes withoutaru saying that there are special rewards available in exchange for badges of gallantry, too.
        I_CAN_SEE_YOUR_LIPS_QUIVERING_AT_THE                                 = 8179,  -- I can see your lips quivering at the thought of receiving such extraordinary spoils!
        BE_ADVISED_WISED_IN_ADVANCE_THAT_YOU_WILL                            = 8180,  -- Be advised-wised in advance that you will lose all your hallmarks and badges of gallantry once the Ambuscade has switched to new content.
        AND_I_M_NOT_SUPPOSED_TO_TELL_YOU                                     = 8181,  -- (...And I'm not supposed to tell you this, but the rewards change as the Ambuscade does.)
        THAT_S_THE_LONG_AND_SHORT_MOSTLY_LONG                                = 8182,  -- That's the long and short--mostly long--of it. Now get those items and try your luck!
        WH_WHAT_S_THIS_YOU_RE_UNFAMILIAR_WITH                                = 8183,  -- Wh-what's this? You're unfamiliar with Records of Eminence? Then firstaru speak with one of our representatives in charge of Eminence to get started.
