        THESE_MISSIVES_PENNED_BY_ABDHALJS_HIMSELF_ARE_INTENDED               = 8204,  -- These missives, penned by Abdhaljs himself, are intended for those adventurers interested in trying their hands at Ambuscade.
        DEAREST_ADVENTURER_LET_ME_FIRST_EXPRESS_MY_HEARTFELT                 = 8205,  -- Dearest adventurer, Let me first express my heartfelt appreciation at your interest in my latest creation. I would exchange pleasantries, but I know what you are most interested in--the spoils. So let's get down to it, hmmm?
